Insider Activity


Individual




David M. Sherbin



Mr. David M. Sherbin is Secretary, Chief Compliance Officer & Senior VP at Delphi Automotive Plc and Secretary, Chief Compliance Officer & Senior VP at Delphi Automotive LLP. He is on the Board of Directors at The Michigan Center For Civic Education and Detroit Symphony Orchestra.
Mr. Sherbin was previously employed as Chief Compliance Officer, VP & General Counsel by Delphi Corp., Secretary, Chief Compliance Officer & Senior VP by Federal-Mogul Corp., Senior Counsel-Corporate Affairs by Heller Financial, Inc., an Associate by Katten Muchin & Zavis, and Secretary, Chief Compliance Officer & VP by Delphi Holdings LLP.
He received his undergraduate degree from Oberlin College and a graduate degree from Cornell Law School.



